<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>石历文转换器 - Lithocal Converter</title>
    <style>
        /* 系统字体，无需网络 */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: "SimSun", "Songti SC", "STSong", "Times New Roman", serif;
            background: #0f0e0c;
            color: #e8e0d0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        /* 背景纹理 - 纯CSS生成，无需图片 */
        .bg-texture {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: 
                repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(0,0,0,0.2) 2px, rgba(0,0,0,0.2) 4px),
                repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 2px, rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 4px);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }
        
        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3d3528;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            color: #c9a961;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(201,169,97,0.3);
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            color: #7a6b55;
            font-size: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.3em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .intro {
            background: rgba(30,28,24,0.8);
            border-left: 4px solid #c9a961;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #a09070;
        }
        
        .input-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(40,36,30,0.9) 0%, rgba(25,23,20,0.9) 100%);
            border: 1px solid #4a4233;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        
        label {
            display: block;
            color: #c9a961;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }
        
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            border: 1px solid #5a5040;
            padding: 15px;
            color: #e8e0d0;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            resize: vertical;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #c9a961;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(201,169,97,0.2);
        }
        
        .controls {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3d3528 0%, #252220 100%);
            border: 2px solid #6b5d4d;
            color: #c9a961;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }
        
        button:hover {
            background: #4a4233;
            border-color: #c9a961;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        
        button:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        
        button.primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a961 0%, #a08040 100%);
            color: #1a1814;
            border-color: #c9a961;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        button.primary:hover {
            background: #d4b76a;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(201,169,97,0.4);
        }
        
        .options {
            margin-left: auto;
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #8b7355;
        }
        
        .option {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        input[type="checkbox"] {
            accent-color: #c9a961;
        }
        
        .output-section {
            background: rgba(20,18,14,0.95);
            border: 2px solid #3d3528;
            padding: 40px;
            min-height: 300px;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        
        .corner {
            position: absolute;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border: 2px solid #c9a961;
            opacity: 0.4;
        }
        
        .corner.tl { top: 10px; left: 10px; border-right: 0; border-bottom: 0; }
        .corner.tr { top: 10px; right: 10px; border-left: 0; border-bottom: 0; }
        .corner.bl { bottom: 10px; left: 10px; border-right: 0; border-top: 0; }
        .corner.br { bottom: 10px; right: 10px; border-left: 0; border-top: 0; }
        
        .output-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #3d3528;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .output-title {
            color: #c9a961;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        }
        
        .glyph-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(90px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .glyph-block {
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            background: #1e1c18;
            border: 2px solid #4a4233;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        
        .glyph-block:hover {
            border-color: #c9a961;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            z-index: 10;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(201,169,97,0.2);
        }
        
        .glyph-block.sacred {
            border: 3px double #c9a961;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a2824 0%, #1e1c18 100%);
        }
        
        .glyph-block.sacred::after {
            content: '◆';
            position: absolute;
            top: -8px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: #c9a961;
            font-size: 10px;
            background: #0f0e0c;
            padding: 0 3px;
        }
        
        .glyph-svg {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            filter: drop-shadow(1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.8));
        }
        
        .glyph-tooltip {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -30px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
            color: #c9a961;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            white-space: nowrap;
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
            z-index: 20;
            border: 1px solid #4a4233;
        }
        
        .glyph-block:hover .glyph-tooltip {
            opacity: 1;
        }
        
        .empty-state {
            text-align: center;
            color: #5a5040;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .info-panel {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border-left: 3px solid #c9a961;
            display: none;
        }
        
        .info-panel.active {
            display: block;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        
        .export-section {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #3d3528;
        }
        
        .usage-guide {
            margin-top: 40px;
            background: rgba(30,28,24,0.6);
            border: 1px solid #3d3528;
            padding: 25px;
        }
        
        .usage-guide h3 {
            color: #c9a961;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .usage-guide ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: #8b7355;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .usage-guide li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            color: #5a5040;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #3d3528;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .controls { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
            .options { margin-left: 0; justify-content: center; margin-top: 10px; }
            .output-section { padding: 20px; }
            .glyph-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(70px, 1fr)); }
        }
        
        .hidden { display: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-texture"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>石历文转换器</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">LITHOCAL CONVERTER</div>
        </header>
        
        <div class="intro">
            <strong>使用说明：</strong>输入简体汉字，转换为受玛雅文明启发的象形文字系统。每个字符都是独立的SVG矢量图形，可直接截图保存或打印。
        </div>
        
        <section class="input-section">
            <label>输入文字（支持常用汉字）：</label>
            <textarea id="inputText" placeholder="例如：日月星辰 山川河流 王者永生...">日月星辰 山川王者</textarea>
            
            <div class="controls">
                <button class="primary" onclick="convertText()">开始转换</button>
                <button onclick="clearText()">清空</button>
                <button onclick="exportResult()">导出图片</button>
                
                <div class="options">
                    <label class="option">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="sacredMode" checked>
                        <span>神圣模式</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="option">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="showTooltip" checked>
                        <span>显示提示</span>
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="output-section" id="captureArea">
            <div class="corner tl"></div>
            <div class="corner tr"></div>
            <div class="corner bl"></div>
            <div class="corner br"></div>
            
            <div class="output-header">
                <span class="output-title">◆ 转换结果 ◆</span>
                <span id="glyphStats" style="color: #6b5d4d; font-size: 0.9rem;"></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="glyph-grid" id="glyphGrid">
                <div class="empty-state">
                    等待输入...<br>
                    <small>在上方输入文字后点击"开始转换"</small>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-panel" id="infoPanel">
                <div style="color: #c9a961; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;" id="infoTitle"></div>
                <div style="color: #8b7355; line-height: 1.6;" id="infoContent"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="export-section">
                <small style="color: #5a5040;">
                    提示：在PC上可右键"另存为"保存此网页；在手机上可截图保存转换结果
                </small>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="usage-guide">
            <h3>可用字符列表</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>天体：</strong>日、月、星、天</li>
                <li><strong>自然：</strong>山、水、火、木、石、土、川、林</li>
                <li><strong>人类：</strong>人、王、神、眼、手、心</li>
                <li><strong>抽象：</strong>永、生、死、时、空、一、二、三</li>
                <li><strong>动物：</strong>龙、鸟、蛇、鱼</li>
                <li><strong>组合：</strong>日月→明、水木→沐、人山→仙</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #6b5d4d; font-size: 0.85rem;">
                * 未收录的字符将显示为占位符。此文件完全离线可用，无需网络连接。
            </p>
        </section>
        
        <footer>
            <p>石历文 - 受玛雅文明启发的新型象形文字系统</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 5px; font-size: 0.8rem;">所有字符均为SVG矢量图形，可无限放大不失真</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

